reviewText: Not worth it. Crap movie. Only wanted to see what actor George Thomas was like. Sorry I purchased.

This has got to be one of the worst low budget movies of its kind. I have never seen such mess. The actors cannot act at all, the sex scences are ridiculous, and the story line is horrible. They should be ashamed of putting this mess on the market to sale. It wasn't even worth the few dollars I spent on it.
